    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被错误地塞进了一艘研究火箭中并发射升空，发现自己已置身于一个全新的世界，在这里你必须掌控模拟系统，努力生存壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个世界会对你的每个行为做出反应。你需要掌控：化学反应、微观温度模拟与对流、液体蒸发等机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要设计建造多种解决方案，通过加工、精炼与建造来突破困境，求得生存并完成使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喔，没准这次多少会有点氧气。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操纵世界</strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/86d769106473754fb29f7ff9d8186b62.poster.avif?t=1763057609\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/86d769106473754fb29f7ff9d8186b62.webm?t=1763057609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/86d769106473754fb29f7ff9d8186b62.mp4?t=1763057609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管你没料到会来这，但你有能力随机应变。在这个新的世界里，你可以创建一个自己的栖息地、发电、制作食物和氧气来生存和壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>实时气体、液体与热量模拟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/5b8b01f3f2148fab776ca1ea2810e644.poster.avif?t=1763057609\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/5b8b01f3f2148fab776ca1ea2810e644.webm?t=1763057609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/5b8b01f3f2148fab776ca1ea2810e644.mp4?t=1763057609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水会流动、蒸发；火焰燃烧需要氧气；每个地块都会模拟热容和导热。如果善用模拟，就能打造出一个动态的基地；否则，后果自负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>种出风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/9f636b69fa78fd8ef46ded8cbe6febee.poster.avif?t=1763057609\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/9f636b69fa78fd8ef46ded8cbe6febee.webm?t=1763057609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168390/extras/9f636b69fa78fd8ef46ded8cbe6febee.mp4?t=1763057609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>所有游戏元素都会对环境产生反应。通过用水、土、种子、创建农田；然后通过操纵模拟来优化产出。</p>",
